<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.2">
<l>cerumiku vāḷe yiṟṟa varavoṉṟu cuṟṟit ticaimaṇṇum viṇṇu muṭaṉē</l>
<l>veruvara veḷḷai veḷḷam muḻutuṅku ḻampa vimaiyōrkaḷ niṉṟu kaṭaiya</l>
<l>paruvarai yoṉṟu niṉṟu mutukiṟpa rantu cuḻalakki ṭantu tuyilum</l>
<l>aruvarai yaṉṉa taṉmai vaṭalāmai yāṉa tirumālna makkō raraṇē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tirumāl was a refuge for us when he became a powerful turtle,</l>
<l rend="indent">[its] nature like a rare mountain,</l>
<l>Which rested lying [still] while a wide mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">standing broadly on its back, whirled,</l>
<l>When the unblinking [celestials], coiling around [it]</l>
<l rend="indent">a serpent with fangs [like] great battle swords,</l>
<l>Kept churning, so that all of the white [milk] sea tossed</l>
<l rend="indent">and the earth in all directions and the heavens were terrified.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
